      "overfit_notes": "BB(20,2) %B with asymmetric thresholds (>0.5 enter, <0.4 exit) plus a hindsight mega-cap universe (top-5 by market cap, which over 2014–2025 maps to AAPL/MSFT/AMZN/GOOGL/META/NVDA). The universe selection adds asset-class fit on top of the simple regime rule.",
      "rules": [
        {
          "label": "Universe",
          "text": "Top 100 stocks by dollar volume → top 5 by market cap (daily refresh)"
        },
        {
          "label": "Regime",
          "text": "BB(20, 2σ) %B(QQQ)"
        },
